caption.p: (A) Annexin V apoptosis assay for compound 7c. SW-620 cells were treated with compound 7c (250 and 500 nM) for 24 h. Quadrant was set for the resulted dots population from the results of the negative auto-fluorescence and the statistical analysis was performed where the significance of data was assessed at p values < 0.05. ** p < 0.01; *** p < 0.001 control vs treated. (B) Annexin V apoptosis assay for compound 7g. SW-620 cells were treated with compound 7g (250 and 500 nM) for 24 h. Quadrant was set for the resulted dots population from the results of the negative auto-fluorescence and the statistical analysis was performed where the significance of data was assessed at p values < 0.05. ** p < 0.01; *** p < 0.001 control vs treated.
